Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:40.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:57.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:58.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:02.82,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:04.29,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:11.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:18.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:27.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:34.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:41.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:48.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:56.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:02:01.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:22.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:26.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I come bearing your doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:35.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That sure was an ominous dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:54.89,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! The Demon Arrives and Wreaks\NHavoc?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:09.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...what about you, Keiichi?\NDidn't you get enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:12.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:18.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! I bet you dreamed that you\ngot dumped by Belldandy, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:21.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:32.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's what I call a good luster...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You have a skilled eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:39.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That one just came in yesterday...\nit's an import.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:49.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A DEMON! A DEMON!\NYOU WILL BECOME A DEMON!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:54.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Did you spot\na great bargain or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Den-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:06.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A CD? What the heck\nare we gonna do with a CD...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:09.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:13.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's good....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember stocking\nanything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:29.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up with this?\NWhy would I have something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to listen to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:35.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But... we don't have a CD player, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:40.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe we should start by\ncoloring it black, just like a record?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where does the needle go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:51.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay\nto spin it at 45 RPM?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.74,0:05:18.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those gods...putting\nextra protection on the seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:23.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And who would stick a CD on a\nfreakin' record player, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:28.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a place is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:36.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am Marller,\NDemon First Class, Unlimited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:40.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And since you did release me\nfrom that claustrophobic CD...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll grant you a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the big idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:53.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you intrude upon our sanctuary\nwithout removing your shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:55.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:06:00.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you're going to ask me for?\nI can't believe your lack of greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:03.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish is granted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that was all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:15.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably a newbie from\nthe shop, trying to drum up sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:26.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I left it behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:28.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:32.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to set foot\nin a place like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:37.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, right now my priority\nis to settle that old score!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:41.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, goddesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:45.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my revenge\nif it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:49.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:56.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}KO{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She beat me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:01.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone better out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:04.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then I'm next!\N{\i1}No, let me take her on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:09.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just get in line. You'll all get\nyour chance with me, so bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! Let's go home right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:21.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Disaster is headed for us...\nI can feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:25.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:27.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're history!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:38.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,O Blue Stone that wards off\nevil and repulses demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I beseech you, protect us\nwith your white robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell me what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:54.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, I felt a certain pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I believe a demon will be coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:00.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:06.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We goddesses serve the Almighty and\nwish for the happiness of all humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:12.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...whereas demons, also known as devils,\nlead them into corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So one of those is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:19.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but I remember\nthis particular pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With Urd's help, I sealed a demon\non the Almighty's orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:27.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's just like the pulse of that demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Registered mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...I'll go answer that, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:34.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:39.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, you mustn't\nleave the barrier field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Demons, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:51.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it's a lot more\nthan just plain hostility...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:54.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right on the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:59.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy and I have\na complex relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:03.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...impenetrable to the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you to talk to me\nlike that, you tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you've forgotten my voice, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:17.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're from my... you were in my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:21.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am Marller,\NDemon First Class, Unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever forget it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:32.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Registered mail... I need you\nto sign for it, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a demon's messenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:38.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see Belldandy's as gullible as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:41.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what am I going to do with\nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did I ever do to upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:48.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you... do you have any idea of the\ntrouble you're causing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:49.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:54.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, it wouldn't be possible\nto bind a goddess to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And you've got two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:59.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In Urd's case,\nit's not that I asked her to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:03.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop making excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:08.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When goddesses loiter around on Earth,\nthe absolute quantity of joy swells.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:10.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, I'll lose my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's way too much happiness\nconcentrated around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To put it bluntly, you're an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:21.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, you'll have to\npay for this with your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:23.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how is that fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:27.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If something were to happen to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:31.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm sure it would bring those\nblasted goddesses to their senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:34.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! You demon! You devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:38.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right. I am a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:42.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll be free to focus on\nmy job without any distractions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:58.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You let your guard down because of\nthat barrier field, huh, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:00.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:04.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I snuck inside before\nyou threw up the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:08.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I was able to\naccomplish my job safely inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done to Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't figured that out?\NHe's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:22.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me!\NMy powers came up short...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and so you were turned\ninto this dreadful form...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that. Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:36.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You will change Keiichi back at once!\nI'm ordering you as a first-class goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't oblige you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:43.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's our job as demons\nto get in the way of you goddesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:47.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle when you\nride him, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:04.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home...\nI just saw Marller back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:09.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:22.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:27.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that Marller always\nhad an evil nature, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that's probably\nwhy she's a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:34.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you sure got your butt kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:39.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, being a bike once in a while\nisn't so bad. You love bikes, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:44.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... hey, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:48.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it would be inconvenient\nfor him to stay this way, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:52.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I promise I'll change\nyou back to your original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:57.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's time for me\nto show my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, drink this and you'll be\nrid of any curse under the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd-Ade Super-Z!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:09.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how can we get him to drink that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:18.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, drink up if you know\nwhat's good for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! You must calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:31.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:35.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it only works on humans....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give it a try this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:43.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Guide this man back to his original\nform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:51.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To break a devil's curse, I guess\nwe're going to need the password.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:56.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if we can keep chipping\naway at it like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:58.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it getting worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:06.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not at all...Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:13.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll do any good\nto give him an extra wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way out of it...Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:27.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind... one way or another,\nwe're going to have to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the password to return\nhim to his original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:36.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our only hope is to get Marller to break\nthe curse and turn him back herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:41.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really think that\ndemon's going to just do as we ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:46.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose Marller's angry\nat us for sealing her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:50.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, we did that\nbecause she broke the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:54.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Marller's the type\nwho never forgets a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:58.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how do you suppose\nthe seal was breached?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:03.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:07.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The catalyst the Almighty\nused to seal Marller...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:10.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet it's around here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:15.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we can just get our hands on it, then\nshe'll have no choice but to do as we say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of Heaven, the Eye of the Earth...\nand the Eye of Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:25.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Reveal to us the location\nof the demon's catalyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:36.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Keiichi, you know what this\nmeans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:40.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then,\nlet's split up and look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:45.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going after the catalyst.\NBelldandy, you try to hunt down Marller.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:52.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll return you to your original form...\nwe promise, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:57.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:10.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:13.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A person dressed like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:24.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Put on a Helmet. Save a Life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:28.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to\nput this on, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right,\nI heard you the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:51.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:16:57.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:59.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:08.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Women are not allowed to enter\nthis dorm! How many times do we...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't be such a stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:14.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys, did you happen\nto buy a strange-looking CD?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:18.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A CD...you think she's\ntalking about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:23.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We unloaded that CD on a\nsecond-hand store ages ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which store was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:29.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better tell me, or I'll give you\nthe punishment of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:32.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The used-record store\nover on Third Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:39.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:44.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better add a new dorm rule...\N''no riding bikes indoors.''
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow some of that stuff\nover there, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:51.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let me have some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:55.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's your own fault\nfor dropping yours, Junpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:58.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you made me drop it, Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:17:59.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:02.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd just drop yours too, Hijiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:03.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:08.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy to grant you that wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:15.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Human misery is a\njoy to behold, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:18.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You feel the same way I'm feeling, aren't\nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:25.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do you a favor by granting your wish,\nand that's the thanks I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:28.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:32.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is all we need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:42.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:48.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, we need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:55.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller, please turn Keiichi\nback to his original form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:59.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You actually think I'm just\ngoing to submit to your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:04.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Surely not the orders of a goddess who\nsealed me in such a horrible catalyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:11.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone like a goddess\nattach herself to a lowly human?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:15.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have a contract with Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can terminate a contract\nwith a human any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:24.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! Because I'm\nstaying here out of my own free will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:29.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I have no choice\nbut to carry out my own duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your feelings for Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:37.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, it's Keiichi's very existence\nthat's binding you to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't I just\nerase Keiichi completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, then you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller, don't you dare go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:50.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then do you want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:58.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at the special effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just like a movie!{\i0}\NWow, look at the special effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:05.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get a move on, now, Keiichi! Power up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:18.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the best you can do as a goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:21.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're weaker\nnow than you were before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:29.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, so that's what's stopping\nyou from releasing your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:32.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must be inconvenient to be a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:37.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Just do as I say and\nturn Keiichi back! Or else I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:41.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You still have the nerve to talk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:45.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you've reached your limit by\nnow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:50.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you break your contract and\ngo back to Heaven, I might forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:53.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller, catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:06.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, you've always been vulnerable\nto good-luck charms, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here, we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:13.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the Almighty's CD!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:17.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The Almighty's catalyst...\npaired with the Demon's catalyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:20.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's what we use to seal away\ndemons who have sinned!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Marller!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:29.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Stop!\NPlease, don't do this to me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:34.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then please give us the password that\nwill return Keiichi to his original form!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:39.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What makes you care about him\nso much? He's nothing but a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:43.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because Keiichi is... because Keiichi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:47.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...someone very important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:50.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:55.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the damned password,\nso back off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.91,0:22:01.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Guide this man back to his original\nform... Ado Solia Helestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:10.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'll get you some clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Belldandy!{\i0}\nI'm sorry, I'll get you some clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:13.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:16.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You saved me!{\i0}\nIs this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:27.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:35.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I get that catalyst back,\nI don't stand a chance against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:40.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really, now!{\i0}\nI've got to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:44.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all Belldandy's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:48.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?\nIsn't this outrageous?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:51.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can I be second-best?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.63,0:22:56.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather sell my soul to the devil\nthan come off second-best to that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:59.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:12.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:24.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:33.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:40.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:46.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:49.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:55.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:24:02.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:08.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.14,0:24:14.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:18.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.23,0:24:34.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The queen's slumber is rudely\ndisturbed by a demon's snore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.07,0:24:38.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When these two meet in bed, it creates\na rift between the man and his goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.27,0:24:41.44,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! Choosing Between\nthe Goddess and the Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.44,0:24:45.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's you I want by my side forever!
